<section id="faq" class="faq section bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container section-title text-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Everything you need to know about joining the RF Technologies team.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="accordion shadow-sm rounded" id="internshipFAQ">

                    <div class="accordion-item border-0 border-bottom">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                            <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                What is the duration of the internship?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#internshipFAQ">
                            <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                                The duration of the internship is exactly <strong>1 month</strong>. It is designed to be highly intensive and focused on practical output.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item border-0 border-bottom">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                Is the internship paid or unpaid?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#internshipFAQ">
                            <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                                The internship itself is unpaid as it focuses heavily on mentorship and learning. However, there is a one-time convenience and processing fee of <strong>₹99 INR</strong> required at the time of final submission.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item border-0 border-bottom">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                Do I need prior experience to apply?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#internshipFAQ">
                            <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                                No prior professional experience is mandatory. We evaluate candidates based on their enthusiasm to learn and their foundational knowledge. Whether you are a beginner or an intermediate coder, we have projects suited to your level.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item border-0">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                Will I receive a certificate?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#internshipFAQ">
                            <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                                Yes. Upon successful completion of your assigned projects and the 1-month tenure, you will receive a verifiable <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong> from RF Technologies, which you can showcase on your resume and LinkedIn profile.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>